Localization.Name: Clark Defense Systems
Localization.Description:
Ground-combat defensive systems, covers a lot of commercial territory from personal armor to defense systems. Naming convention tend to be pretty straight-forward and logical.

Models: PAB-4 (Personal Ablative/Ballistic Light Armor)

Localization.Name: FBL-8u Undersuit Imperial Red
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Undersuit
Damage Reduction: 10%
Temp. Rating: -30 / 60 °C
Radiation Protection: 15200 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 81 REM/s

The FBL-8u is the first CDS undersuit to utilize the manufacturers new orb-weave technology that produces an impressively light yet strong material that can withstand the rigors of space travel. Originally developed to pair perfectly with CDS's FBL-8a light armor, it remains compatible with other armor sets.
